cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for real-time exposure control of a mobile camera. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also extensively uses reinforcement learning, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of neural networks for exposure prediction and Gaussian policy gradient for training suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with multimedia applications, which may fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper deals with camera control and image processing, which may fall under cs.GR (Graphics).
